#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.27"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga "
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.27:0.3"
msgid "27. Samattasutta "
msgstr "27. Completely "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn47.27:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ. "
msgstr "The same setting. "

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto āyasmantaṃ anuruddhaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.27:1.3"
msgid "“‘asekho, asekho’ti, āvuso anuruddha, vuccati. "
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of this person called ‘an adept’. "

msgctxt "sn47.27:1.4"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, asekho hotī”ti? "
msgstr "How is an adept defined?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.27:1.5"
msgid "“Catunnaṃ kho, āvuso, satipaṭṭhānānaṃ samattaṃ bhāvitattā asekho hoti. "
msgstr "“Reverends, an adept is someone who has completely developed the four kinds of mindfulness meditation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn47.27:2.1"
msgid "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.2"
msgid "Idhāvuso, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.27:2.6"
msgid "Imesaṃ kho, āvuso, catunnaṃ satipaṭṭhānānaṃ samattaṃ bhāvitattā asekho hotī”ti. "
msgstr "An adept is someone who has completely developed the four kinds of mindfulness meditation.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.27:2.7"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
